data.description: Stunning Home in Tuloso Midway ISD! Situated at the end of a quiet street, this 2021 construction welcomes you into this immaculate home, boasting tons of builder upgrades! The large entry opens into your spacious living area, with tons of windows for abundant natural light and tile flooring throughout for easy maintenance! The open layout ensures ease of entertaining, with quick access to the kitchen and dining space. The roomy kitchen is complete with quartz counters, a gorgeous backsplash, and tons of cabinet storage! The huge Master Suite is complete with an En-suite Master Bathroom, while two secondary bedrooms affords space for everyone to unwind! The extended patio off the living room is fully screened, allowing for relaxing afternoons in the shade, or hang out in your backyard, with privacy fencing to ensure quiet enjoyment! Located in the sought-after Tuloso Midway school district, with quick access to both I-37 and TX-44! Schedule a showing today!
